        <remarks>
          <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="5265d-118">如果 <xref:System.Web.UI.RoleServiceManager.LoadRoles%2A> 属性设置为 `true`，则 <xref:System.Web.UI.RoleServiceManager> 类使用 <xref:System.Web.Security.Roles.GetRolesForUser%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 方法检索角色列表。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5265d-118">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.RoleServiceManager.LoadRoles%2A> property is set to `true`, the list of roles is retrieved by the <xref:System.Web.UI.RoleServiceManager> class by using the <xref:System.Web.Security.Roles.GetRolesForUser%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5265d-119">然后，将列表序列化为页标记。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5265d-119">The list is then serialized into the page markup.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="5265d-120">`true`<xref:System.Web.UI.RoleServiceManager.LoadRoles%2A> 时，当前已验证身份的用户所属的所有角色都将发送到浏览器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5265d-120">When <xref:System.Web.UI.RoleServiceManager.LoadRoles%2A> is `true`, all the roles that the current authenticated user belongs to are sent to the browser.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5265d-121">由于用户可能会看到角色信息，这可能是一个安全问题。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5265d-121">Because users can potentially see the role information, this can be a security issue.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5265d-122"><xref:System.Web.UI.RoleServiceManager.LoadRoles%2A> 属性可以在 <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> 控件中指定，也可以在关联的 <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> 控件中指定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5265d-122">The <xref:System.Web.UI.RoleServiceManager.LoadRoles%2A> property can be specified in the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control or in an associated <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5265d-123">如果为代理实例将 <xref:System.Web.UI.RoleServiceManager.LoadRoles%2A> 设置为 `true`，则将检索角色的列表并将其添加到页面中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5265d-123">If <xref:System.Web.UI.RoleServiceManager.LoadRoles%2A> is set to `true` for a proxy instance, the list of roles is retrieved and added to the page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5265d-124">如果 `false`<xref:System.Web.UI.RoleServiceManager.LoadRoles%2A>，则不会向页面标记添加角色。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5265d-124">If <xref:System.Web.UI.RoleServiceManager.LoadRoles%2A> is `false`, the roles are not added to the page markup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5265d-125">在这种情况下，可以使用方法在浏览器中将角色信息存储在内存中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5265d-125">In that case, you can use the  method to store role information in memory in the browser.</span></span>  
  
